-- Inserir integração demo do Strava para userId 1
INSERT INTO user_integrations (userId, provider, accessToken, refreshToken, expiresAt, isActive, metadata, createdAt, updatedAt)
VALUES (1, 'strava', 'demo_access_token', 'demo_refresh_token', UNIX_TIMESTAMP(DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 6 HOUR)) * 1000, 1, JSON_OBJECT('athlete_id', 'demo_athlete_123', 'username', 'demo_triathlete'), NOW(), NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE updatedAt = NOW();

-- Inserir atividades demo realistas
INSERT INTO activities (userId, provider, externalId, name, type, distance, duration, startDate, avgHeartRate, maxHeartRate, calories, createdAt, updatedAt) VALUES
(1, 'strava', 'demo_1', 'Treino Intervalado Matinal', 'Run', 10.50, 3240, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), 165.00, 182, 850, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_2', 'Ciclismo Longo - Preparação Ironman', 'Ride', 85.00, 10800, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 2 DAY), 142.00, 168, 2400, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_3', 'Natação Técnica', 'Swim', 2.00, 2400, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 3 DAY), NULL, NULL, 600, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_4', 'Corrida Recuperação', 'Run', 8.00, 3000, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 4 DAY), 138.00, 152, 650, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_5', 'Brick: Bike + Run', 'Workout', 45.00, 7200, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 5 DAY), 155.00, 175, 1800, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_6', 'Treino de Força + Corrida', 'Run', 5.00, 1800, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 6 DAY), 148.00, 165, 450, NOW(), NOW()),
(1, 'strava', 'demo_7', 'Ciclismo Intervalos', 'Ride', 60.00, 7200, DATE_SUB(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY), 158.00, 178, 1600, NOW(), NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE updatedAt = NOW();
